OL,3,CSpeed enforcement measures proposed
OL,4,Cfor Helston Culdrose road
OL,6,FPeople in Cornwall are being invited
OL,7,Fto share their views on proposals to
OL,8,Finstall average speed cameras on a
OL,9,Fstretch of the A3083 in Helston and to
OL,10,Freduce the speed limit from 60mph to
OL,11,F50mph, on the section of road running
OL,12,Falongside RNAS Culdrose.
OL,14,FAlmost 2,000 residents signed a
OL,15,Fpetition calling for speed enforcement
OL,16,Fon the road after the last fatal
OL,17,Fcollision.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
