OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772701496
OL,3,CSpeed enforcement measures proposed
OL,4,Cfor Helston Culdrose road
OL,6,FDaniel Thirkhill, who started the
OL,7,Fpetition, told ITV Westcountry that
OL,8,F"this change is to save lives and
OL,9,Fneeds to happen".
OL,11,FIn November 2025 Cornwall Coroner Guy
OL,12,FDavies stated that action was needed
OL,13,Fon this road to prevent further deaths.
OL,15,FThe head of road safety at Devon and
OL,16,FCornwall Police, Adrian Leisk, said
OL,17,Fthat the community had "rightly called
OL,18,Ffor action" after "numerous serious
OL,19,Fand fatal crashes" involving excess
OL,20,Fspeed.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@PO]yD@XOUzD@KO]zD@SOU{D@RO]
