OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772701496
OL,3,CSpeed enforcement measures proposed
OL,4,Cfor Helston Culdrose road
OL,6,FHe added: "Average Speed Camera
OL,7,Fsystems are extremely effective at
OL,8,Flowering speeds. Our sites throughout
OL,9,FDevon & Cornwall have a compliance
OL,10,Frate of over 99%. We are proud to be
OL,11,Fworking with Cornwall Council to help
OL,12,Ffund this scheme, which we believe
OL,13,Fwill save lives in this area."
OL,15,FThe proposed safety measures would be
OL,16,Fjointly funded by Cornwall Council and
OL,17,Fthe Vision Zero South West Partnership.
OL,26,@nD@KOU
