CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772701496
OL,3,CSpeed enforcement measures proposed
OL,4,Cfor Helston Culdrose road
OL,6,FCornwall Council data showed that the
OL,7,Fmajority of drivers are travelling at,
OL,8,For below, 52mph along this section of
OL,9,Froad which suggests that lowering the
OL,10,Flimit is unlikely to affect journey
OL,11,Ftimes.
OL,13,FDan Rogerson, Cornwall Council cabinet
OL,14,Fmember for transport said that "one
OL,15,Fperson killed on our roads is one too
OL,16,Fmany" and that "this is a scheme that
OL,17,Fwe have wanted to bring forward for
OL,18,Fsome time".
OL,20,FThe consultation on the proposals is
OL,21,Fopen until 19 March.
OL,26,@vD@`OUxD@EO]xD@POU
